{"tid":2099351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"網上識人係咪好難會有feel?","createTime":"2020-07-08T07:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T10:05:36.000Z","uid":318802,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"db84156b2fa9bc4caa935301de1f5fa70b168a95","tid":2099351,"uid":318802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"唔知點解總係會覺得網上識到既人有一種距離感<br />\n大家之間冇共同既回憶<br />\n冇一個感情基礎<br />\n約左出黎之後就唔係好想約下次<br />\n<br />\n之前約過一個網上識既女仔出黎食下飯<br />\n但係成程都冇心動既感覺<br />\n到底係咪我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然食完飯之後都仲有keep住傾<br />\n但係已經冇乜動力再約佢出黎"},{"pid":"d9ecf4133639e389f0c3faa8f80000855173990a","tid":2099351,"uid":48500,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"次序唔一樣<br />\n現實係朋友&gt;拍拖&gt;攪野<br />\n上網係攪野&gt;拍拖&gt;朋友"},{"pid":"3a7ead2ebac0598414673a9f1a1bf172996d27db","tid":2099351,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"所有野都講緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827adda28763c6f61a7752715e866214ae5e53f","tid":2099351,"uid":353819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"可能佢唔夠靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226a9a572a2d9fc1412a7c8a3f8e194166e94d00","tid":2099351,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<br />\n<br />\n全部ex+現任都上網識<br />\n現實慢熱同唔點講野，仲難識人"},{"pid":"9206b412aeff59cf55e52ad44a8f9570f31ba246","tid":2099351,"uid":318802,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"d9ecf4133639e389f0c3faa8f80000855173990a","tid":2099351,"uid":48500,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"次序唔一樣<br />\n現實係朋友&gt;拍拖&gt;攪野<br />\n上網係攪野&gt;拍拖&gt;朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"都岩<br />\n網上約人太有目的性<br />\n我心入面成日諗約出去當識多個朋友咁<br />\n但通常都會下意識咁用左可發展對象既標準去評估對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2f2830aa210a4c1950614e4e05d4679f8228db","tid":2099351,"uid":318802,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b827adda28763c6f61a7752715e866214ae5e53f","tid":2099351,"uid":353819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"可能佢唔夠靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"我都唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一眼見到佢覺得普普通通<br />\n反而佢除左口罩之後有少少包包面反而幾cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40baa45c7bb994b2bf05101f09e1b4c64cc7fd17","tid":2099351,"uid":318802,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"226a9a572a2d9fc1412a7c8a3f8e194166e94d00","tid":2099351,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<br />\n<br />\n全部ex+現任都上網識<br />\n現實慢熱同唔點講野，仲難識人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"我自己會覺得網上識人好速食<br />\n對對方既好感快黎快去<br />\n好難可以用長時間去互相磨合"},{"pid":"65edf292d6482deb8d440e7af5b68c6bb983b968","tid":2099351,"uid":300620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"差唔多，只係平時你會有feel 先"},{"pid":"d19951e15d91a4bee2dcacb888687651488278e0","tid":2099351,"uid":200037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"做朋友姐"},{"pid":"24f5bc1748e18447986e13a7f081ad5be03931df","tid":2099351,"uid":229607,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"40baa45c7bb994b2bf05101f09e1b4c64cc7fd17","tid":2099351,"uid":318802,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"226a9a572a2d9fc1412a7c8a3f8e194166e94d00","tid":2099351,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<br />\n<br />\n全部ex+現任都上網識<br />\n現實慢熱同唔點講野，仲難識人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:45:05